1
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:38,970
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,970 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 7=

3
00:00:58,970 --> 00:01:01,720
(Guan Yunfeng,
Eighth-Rank Black-Robed Head Constable)

4
00:01:03,791 --> 00:01:04,875
Enforcement Division,
Ministry of Justice.

5
00:01:05,416 --> 00:01:06,583
We've been waiting for you.

6
00:01:07,833 --> 00:01:09,583
You Ministry scum.

7
00:01:10,208 --> 00:01:11,875
(Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee, No. 5)
You think you can arrest me?

8
00:01:14,416 --> 00:01:15,291
You're Diaotu,

9
00:01:15,291 --> 00:01:17,333
the Flower-Picking Bee,
No. 5 on the List.

10
00:01:18,041 --> 00:01:18,416
Get him.

11
00:01:52,875 --> 00:01:54,666
(Enforcement, Ministry of Justice)
Useless fools. Useless!

12
00:01:54,875 --> 00:01:55,666
All these men,

13
00:01:55,708 --> 00:01:57,833
and you let a lecherous bandit escape?

14
00:01:59,375 --> 00:02:00,000
Guan Yunfeng.

15
00:02:00,083 --> 00:02:01,791
What's wrong with you?

16
00:02:03,916 --> 00:02:05,041
I failed in my duty.

17
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,291
Please punish me, Chief Constable.

18
00:02:07,291 --> 00:02:08,708
At least you know
you should be punished!

19
00:02:08,708 --> 00:02:09,958
Guan Yunfeng failed to catch the thief.

20
00:02:09,958 --> 00:02:10,625
By rule, he must be punished.

21
00:02:10,875 --> 00:02:11,375
Take him away.

22
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,333
Give him 20 heavy strokes!

23
00:02:13,916 --> 00:02:15,500
Chief, Diaotu is a lecherous fiend

24
00:02:15,583 --> 00:02:16,458
and highly skilled.

25
00:02:16,458 --> 00:02:17,750
Constable Guan did his best.

26
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:18,541
Yes, Chief Constable.

27
00:02:18,541 --> 00:02:20,083
Anyone who pleads for him again

28
00:02:20,458 --> 00:02:22,000
will share his punishment.

29
00:02:23,416 --> 00:02:24,208
Guys,

30
00:02:24,916 --> 00:02:26,000
don't plead for me.

31
00:02:26,583 --> 00:02:27,666
I failed in my duty.

32
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:29,916
I accept my punishment.

33
00:02:32,708 --> 00:02:33,458
Do it!

34
00:02:35,791 --> 00:02:36,458
Diaotu,

35
00:02:37,333 --> 00:02:38,375
I won't rest

36
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,041
until I catch you.

37
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:42,350
(Northern Bureau)

38
00:02:45,208 --> 00:02:46,625
Miss, is your surname Shen?

39
00:02:47,208 --> 00:02:48,625
Yes. How did you know?

40
00:02:48,625 --> 00:02:49,833
There's a letter for you.

41
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,333
Thank you.

42
00:02:55,890 --> 00:02:58,430
(Feng Fuliu)

43
00:03:05,791 --> 00:03:06,708
I came as promised.

44
00:03:06,958 --> 00:03:07,791
Show yourself.

45
00:03:12,666 --> 00:03:13,708
Congratulations, Miss Shen.

46
00:03:13,708 --> 00:03:15,000
You passed the assessment.

47
00:03:16,208 --> 00:03:16,666
Thank you.

48
00:03:18,083 --> 00:03:18,958
Is that all?

49
00:03:19,791 --> 00:03:21,083
Nothing else to say to me?

50
00:03:23,958 --> 00:03:24,625
Feng Fuliu.

51
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:26,875
I have joined the Northern Bureau.

52
00:03:27,583 --> 00:03:30,000
From now on, we are sworn enemies.

53
00:03:31,875 --> 00:03:32,583
What are you laughing at?

54
00:03:33,375 --> 00:03:34,000
Officer Shen,

55
00:03:34,791 --> 00:03:35,958
in your eyes,

56
00:03:38,166 --> 00:03:39,666
am I truly so unforgivable?

57
00:03:40,291 --> 00:03:41,708
I don't care what kind of man you are.

58
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:43,583
What matters is

59
00:03:44,291 --> 00:03:45,833
that you are No. 2 on the Bounty List,

60
00:03:46,708 --> 00:03:48,458
a wanted fugitive of the court.

61
00:03:48,958 --> 00:03:50,291
I am an officer. You are a thief.

62
00:03:50,708 --> 00:03:52,583
Catching you is only right.

63
00:03:54,833 --> 00:03:56,083
You're still too naive.

64
00:03:56,625 --> 00:03:58,333
Once you spend more time in the Bureau,

65
00:03:58,833 --> 00:03:59,416
you'll understand

66
00:04:00,375 --> 00:04:01,875
that this world
is not only black and white.

67
00:04:03,375 --> 00:04:04,291
There is gray too.

68
00:04:04,875 --> 00:04:05,750
In my eyes,

69
00:04:06,291 --> 00:04:08,083
there is only black and white. No gray.

70
00:04:08,416 --> 00:04:10,041
Then you'll never catch Leng Xin

71
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,541
and avenge your father.

72
00:04:12,208 --> 00:04:13,000
How do you know that?

73
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:14,125
Who exactly are you?

74
00:04:15,375 --> 00:04:16,041
Me?

75
00:04:17,375 --> 00:04:18,708
I am Feng Fuliu,

76
00:04:18,708 --> 00:04:20,875
the phantom thief
ranked No. 2 on the List.

77
00:04:21,958 --> 00:04:22,416
But

78
00:04:23,583 --> 00:04:24,375
I'm also your friend.

79
00:04:25,291 --> 00:04:26,333
Since you walk the criminal path,

80
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,041
we can never be friends.

81
00:04:34,083 --> 00:04:35,375
You don't want to be my friend?

82
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,541
Then what do you want to be?

83
00:04:39,041 --> 00:04:40,041
Enemies. That's all.

84
00:04:47,166 --> 00:04:48,625
You're still so impatient.

85
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,166
If you can't change that,

86
00:04:50,166 --> 00:04:51,916
you may never uncover the truth.

87
00:04:53,083 --> 00:04:53,833
Who are you?

88
00:04:55,666 --> 00:04:56,833
(Feng Fuliu.)

89
00:04:57,916 --> 00:04:59,083
(Chang Beiming.)

90
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,791
(Sun Manor)

91
00:05:01,791 --> 00:05:02,791
(Sun Manor)
You may go back.

92
00:05:02,791 --> 00:05:03,250
(Sun Manor)
Yes.

93
00:05:06,958 --> 00:05:07,500
Who are you?

94
00:05:08,291 --> 00:05:09,875
Help!

95
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:12,930
(Enforcement Division,
Ministry of Justice)

96
00:05:13,916 --> 00:05:17,083
My poor daughter!

97
00:05:17,083 --> 00:05:19,958
You died so horribly!

98
00:05:21,083 --> 00:05:22,458
Here in the capital,

99
00:05:22,666 --> 00:05:23,875
under the Emperor's very nose,

100
00:05:24,833 --> 00:05:26,416
that monster is getting bolder
by the day.

101
00:05:26,875 --> 00:05:29,375
He attacked the Vice Minister
of Rites' manor.

102
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,666
(Duan Li, Southern Bureau's Commander)
What's the Ministry of Justice doing?

103
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:35,875
Commander Duan, Vice Minister Sun,

104
00:05:35,916 --> 00:05:38,125
we're doing everything to catch him.

105
00:05:38,375 --> 00:05:40,833
But he is highly skilled.

106
00:05:40,958 --> 00:05:43,291
So we haven't...

107
00:05:44,875 --> 00:05:45,500
Brother,

108
00:05:46,166 --> 00:05:46,875
you must

109
00:05:47,291 --> 00:05:51,375
seek justice for your niece!

110
00:05:52,333 --> 00:05:53,416
Chief Constable Lin,

111
00:05:54,208 --> 00:05:55,083
if you fail

112
00:05:55,583 --> 00:05:57,500
to give me an answer for this,

113
00:05:58,125 --> 00:06:01,208
I'll report you
before His Majesty myself.

114
00:06:01,958 --> 00:06:03,041
Useless fool.

115
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:04,791
Apologize to Commander Duan

116
00:06:05,208 --> 00:06:06,500
and Vice Minister Sun. Now!

117
00:06:07,625 --> 00:06:08,416
I have failed you.

118
00:06:08,666 --> 00:06:10,250
You certainly have.

119
00:06:10,416 --> 00:06:11,250
From now on,

120
00:06:11,458 --> 00:06:13,541
your Enforcement Division
is off this case.

121
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:15,416
I'll petition the court

122
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,166
to put the Jinyiwei in charge.

123
00:06:17,375 --> 00:06:18,916
(Northern Bureau)
A depraved criminal runs rampant,

124
00:06:19,541 --> 00:06:21,125
terrorizing the imperial capital.

125
00:06:21,875 --> 00:06:23,833
(Imperial Edict)
The Ministry of Justice has failed.

126
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:27,041
(Imperial Edict)
Lin Feng is dismissed pending review.

127
00:06:27,458 --> 00:06:30,458
The Jinyiwei Northern Bureau
is hereby ordered

128
00:06:30,916 --> 00:06:33,000
to take full charge of the Diaotu case.

129
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,708
(Imperial Edict)
to take full charge of the Diaotu case.

130
00:06:34,708 --> 00:06:36,333
Within ten days,

131
00:06:36,583 --> 00:06:38,375
the Northern Bureau needs
to capture the criminal

132
00:06:38,833 --> 00:06:40,625
and uphold the law.

133
00:06:42,166 --> 00:06:43,375
These criminals are out of control.

134
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:46,416
They even dared target
an official from the Ministry of Rites.

135
00:06:47,125 --> 00:06:49,916
His Majesty and the Cabinet
have set a deadline.

136
00:06:53,333 --> 00:06:53,916
Guokai,

137
00:06:54,416 --> 00:06:55,625
I think this case

138
00:06:56,083 --> 00:06:57,625
should go to the female Jinyiwei.

139
00:07:00,125 --> 00:07:00,708
My lord,

140
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,083
we're dealing with

141
00:07:03,291 --> 00:07:05,000
a predator who preys on women.

142
00:07:05,166 --> 00:07:05,458
Well...

143
00:07:06,125 --> 00:07:07,250
Having the female guards handle it

144
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,000
doesn't seem appropriate.

145
00:07:10,625 --> 00:07:12,416
I think they're

146
00:07:12,541 --> 00:07:13,541
exactly right for it.

147
00:07:13,583 --> 00:07:13,833
But

148
00:07:14,208 --> 00:07:15,958
they just started.
They have no experience.

149
00:07:15,958 --> 00:07:16,958
If you never use them,

150
00:07:16,958 --> 00:07:18,583
how will they get any?

151
00:07:18,583 --> 00:07:20,333
Fine, fine. Use them.

152
00:07:21,041 --> 00:07:21,833
Someone.

153
00:07:21,833 --> 00:07:22,208
Yes!

154
00:07:22,416 --> 00:07:25,458
Summon Shen Bingfan, Hua Mange,
and Cheng Xintian.

155
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,041
Greetings, Commander.

156
00:07:40,583 --> 00:07:42,208
Greetings, Commissioner.

157
00:07:42,375 --> 00:07:45,000
Soldiers are trained for years

158
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:46,166
for one moment of need.

159
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:48,083
Now this predator is running wild.

160
00:07:48,333 --> 00:07:49,500
He even dares to harm

161
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:51,583
the family of a court official.

162
00:07:51,791 --> 00:07:53,250
He has no fear of the law

163
00:07:53,458 --> 00:07:54,500
and deserves no mercy.

164
00:07:54,791 --> 00:07:57,375
The first case I assign to you

165
00:07:57,833 --> 00:08:01,458
is to capture Diaotu,
the Flower-Picking Bee.

166
00:08:02,041 --> 00:08:02,833
I give you

167
00:08:02,958 --> 00:08:04,000
ten days.

168
00:08:04,416 --> 00:08:06,500
If you catch him within the deadline,

169
00:08:07,625 --> 00:08:08,500
you will be richly rewarded.

170
00:08:08,916 --> 00:08:10,000
If you fail,

171
00:08:10,458 --> 00:08:14,041
go back where you came from.

172
00:08:15,208 --> 00:08:16,333
Ten days?

173
00:08:17,041 --> 00:08:18,833
Where are we supposed to find him
in ten days?

174
00:08:19,375 --> 00:08:20,125
Within ten days,

175
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:21,291
I will capture Diaotu.

176
00:08:21,791 --> 00:08:22,458
Good.

177
00:08:23,666 --> 00:08:25,333
If you don't catch Diaotu in ten days,

178
00:08:25,625 --> 00:08:27,458
the three of you can resign.

179
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,640
(Northern Bureau)

180
00:08:30,708 --> 00:08:32,166
Why did you agree

181
00:08:32,375 --> 00:08:34,375
to solve it in ten days
without asking us?

182
00:08:34,375 --> 00:08:35,333
Because I'm confident.

183
00:08:35,541 --> 00:08:37,125
I'll capture Diaotu within ten days.

184
00:08:37,416 --> 00:08:38,916
Who do you think Diaotu is?

185
00:08:39,375 --> 00:08:41,291
He's No. 5 on the Bounty List.

186
00:08:41,458 --> 00:08:43,500
Liu Sankong nearly got you killed.

187
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:44,833
You're no match for Diaotu.

188
00:08:45,458 --> 00:08:46,583
Do you know Diaotu well?

189
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,625
Me?

190
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:49,666
I don't.

191
00:08:50,125 --> 00:08:51,208
But I know this.

192
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,000
No. 5 on the Bounty List

193
00:08:53,166 --> 00:08:54,083
is no easy target.

194
00:08:54,666 --> 00:08:55,458
Bingfan,

195
00:08:55,958 --> 00:08:57,875
let's think this through.

196
00:08:58,791 --> 00:08:59,875
(Northern Bureau)
Yes, Bingfan.

197
00:09:00,083 --> 00:09:02,166
(Northern Bureau)
At least ask the Commander

198
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:03,916
to assign us some male Jinyiwei.

199
00:09:05,458 --> 00:09:06,250
This is the first mission

200
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:07,708
the Commander gave us.

201
00:09:08,125 --> 00:09:09,291
How can we ask the men for help?

202
00:09:09,666 --> 00:09:11,458
You're not planning
to do this alone again, are you?

203
00:09:12,250 --> 00:09:15,041
Bingfan, we're a team.
We do this together.

204
00:09:20,458 --> 00:09:21,583
What do we do, Hua?

205
00:09:23,291 --> 00:09:24,250
This won't work.

206
00:09:24,791 --> 00:09:26,083
We need to borrow some men.

207
00:09:26,416 --> 00:09:28,083
Everyone in the Northern Bureau
answers to Mr. Lu.

208
00:09:28,291 --> 00:09:29,708
What if he refuses?

209
00:09:29,875 --> 00:09:30,833
Not necessarily.

210
00:09:31,333 --> 00:09:32,708
We don't have to borrow Jinyiwei.

211
00:09:35,416 --> 00:09:37,458
Hua, Xintian, I found something out.

212
00:09:38,041 --> 00:09:39,125
Constable Guan Yunfeng
of the Enforcement Division

213
00:09:39,166 --> 00:09:40,458
failed to catch Diaotu.

214
00:09:40,875 --> 00:09:41,791
Not only was he caned,

215
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:43,833
but he was also scolded in public
by the Chief Constable.

216
00:09:44,041 --> 00:09:44,541
Now,

217
00:09:44,625 --> 00:09:46,541
after hearing the Jinyiwei
took over the Diaotu case,

218
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,958
he's too angry to eat or drink.

219
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:51,333
I was thinking we could join forces
with him

220
00:09:51,625 --> 00:09:53,500
and borrow a few skilled men
from the Enforcement Division.

221
00:09:54,166 --> 00:09:55,791
Then we might stand a chance
against Diaotu.

222
00:09:57,458 --> 00:09:59,000
But why would he help us?

223
00:10:01,125 --> 00:10:02,208
Because I'll make him.

224
00:10:03,083 --> 00:10:05,125
Diaotu, I'll make sure
you die horribly.

225
00:10:07,416 --> 00:10:08,416
Hey, handsome.

226
00:10:08,708 --> 00:10:10,958
Drinking your sorrows away alone?

227
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:11,875
Get lost.

228
00:10:12,125 --> 00:10:12,916
Go hustle somewhere else.

229
00:10:13,208 --> 00:10:13,666
What?

230
00:10:14,208 --> 00:10:15,208
What do you take me for?

231
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:17,916
Duoyu.

232
00:10:17,916 --> 00:10:18,416
Guan.

233
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:21,750
Xu.

234
00:10:22,166 --> 00:10:23,000
You misunderstand.

235
00:10:23,333 --> 00:10:24,000
This is Hua.

236
00:10:24,208 --> 00:10:26,416
She's a Squad Leader
from Jinyiwei Northern Bureau.

237
00:10:29,375 --> 00:10:30,125
A female Jinyiwei?

238
00:10:33,166 --> 00:10:34,333
The Northern Bureau
really recruited women?

239
00:10:35,666 --> 00:10:36,416
Not only that,

240
00:10:36,958 --> 00:10:37,416
but

241
00:10:37,666 --> 00:10:38,958
the mission to catch Diaotu

242
00:10:39,250 --> 00:10:40,708
has been given to Hua and her team.

243
00:10:41,375 --> 00:10:42,166
Take a look around.

244
00:10:43,291 --> 00:10:44,541
That's absurd.

245
00:10:44,833 --> 00:10:46,000
Diaotu is vicious.

246
00:10:46,666 --> 00:10:48,041
How can they send women after him?

247
00:10:48,666 --> 00:10:50,208
Exactly.

248
00:10:50,625 --> 00:10:53,500
That's why we came to you for help,
Constable Guan.

249
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:56,458
When it comes to catching that scum,

250
00:10:58,083 --> 00:10:59,166
I will do my duty.

251
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:01,916
Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee.

252
00:11:02,041 --> 00:11:02,833
Diaotu?

253
00:11:05,958 --> 00:11:07,250
Tell me everything you know.

254
00:11:08,666 --> 00:11:11,750
Zhu Zijun, daughter of Mr. Zhu
from the east-side gold shop.

255
00:11:30,458 --> 00:11:32,416
Beauty, here I come.

256
00:11:42,583 --> 00:11:43,375
Who are you?

257
00:11:43,791 --> 00:11:44,875
Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee.

258
00:11:45,291 --> 00:11:46,166
Assaulting women,

259
00:11:46,416 --> 00:11:47,291
abduction, and plunder.

260
00:11:47,791 --> 00:11:49,291
73 lives on your hands.

261
00:11:49,541 --> 00:11:51,000
The reward is 5,000 taels.

262
00:11:51,333 --> 00:11:52,125
Dead or alive.

263
00:11:54,083 --> 00:11:55,166
You are a bounty hunter.

264
00:11:55,791 --> 00:11:57,666
But you got one thing wrong.

265
00:11:58,250 --> 00:11:59,166
After tonight,

266
00:11:59,666 --> 00:12:01,375
it'll be 74 lives.

267
00:12:12,833 --> 00:12:13,458
Are you all right?

268
00:12:30,791 --> 00:12:31,458
A skilled fighter.

269
00:12:36,791 --> 00:12:37,750
Constable Guan, are you all right?

270
00:12:38,208 --> 00:12:38,583
I'm fine.

271
00:12:40,375 --> 00:12:40,958
I'll go after him.

272
00:12:42,375 --> 00:12:43,625
Hua, be careful!

273
00:12:44,625 --> 00:12:45,208
Bingfan...

274
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,750
You know martial arts?

275
00:12:48,875 --> 00:12:49,958
I never said I didn't.

276
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:51,541
I just don't like fighting.

277
00:13:07,666 --> 00:13:08,833
There's a distinctive scent.

278
00:13:12,916 --> 00:13:13,750
What a strange smell.

279
00:13:16,208 --> 00:13:16,500
Hold this.

280
00:13:19,333 --> 00:13:19,958
I can walk myself.

281
00:13:19,958 --> 00:13:20,333
Don't move.

282
00:13:21,875 --> 00:13:22,833
Put me down.

283
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:28,770
(Yin Manor)

284
00:13:33,875 --> 00:13:35,250
You love acting alone, don't you?

285
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:36,375
Always playing the hero?

286
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:38,291
Listen, Shen Bingfan.

287
00:13:38,541 --> 00:13:40,250
You only have one life.

288
00:13:40,583 --> 00:13:41,625
If you don't value it,

289
00:13:41,916 --> 00:13:43,125
no one else can value it for you.

290
00:13:44,333 --> 00:13:45,250
I'm warning you, Shen Bingfan.

291
00:13:45,666 --> 00:13:46,541
If you keep this up,

292
00:13:47,041 --> 00:13:48,833
hurting yourself
and dragging down the team,

293
00:13:49,208 --> 00:13:50,083
I'll tell Zhang Weimin

294
00:13:51,166 --> 00:13:52,333
to strike you from the Jinyiwei roster.

295
00:13:52,833 --> 00:13:53,708
What did I do wrong?

296
00:13:53,875 --> 00:13:54,500
Be quiet.

297
00:13:55,041 --> 00:13:55,958
Think about it yourself.

298
00:13:59,291 --> 00:14:00,750
Cheng Xintian, where's the medicine?

299
00:14:01,166 --> 00:14:02,083
Coming.

300
00:14:02,541 --> 00:14:04,041
I saw you two arguing,

301
00:14:04,041 --> 00:14:05,625
so I didn't dare come in.

302
00:14:05,791 --> 00:14:06,791
- We weren't.
- We weren't.

303
00:14:08,458 --> 00:14:09,000
Leave us.

304
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:17,208
Bear with it. I'll apply the medicine.

305
00:14:18,541 --> 00:14:19,375
I'll do it myself.

306
00:14:19,541 --> 00:14:20,250
Be quiet.

307
00:14:21,458 --> 00:14:22,291
Stay still.

308
00:14:22,810 --> 00:14:27,520
♪In a fleeting moment♪

309
00:14:28,890 --> 00:14:33,180
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

310
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:40,060
♪Whose name is it♪

311
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:45,520
♪I whisper in my heart♪

312
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:53,020
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

313
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:56,640
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

314
00:14:56,640 --> 00:15:00,180
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

315
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:04,430
♪A fate that cannot be severed♪

316
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,770
♪Round and round♪

317
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:12,430
♪Threads of love bind us together♪

318
00:15:12,430 --> 00:15:17,270
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

319
00:15:18,470 --> 00:15:24,970
♪Afraid memories
will vanish like dreams♪

320
00:15:24,970 --> 00:15:28,680
♪This longing I cannot say♪

321
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:33,890
♪I wish you could hear♪

322
00:15:56,500 --> 00:15:56,875
Bingfan.

323
00:16:03,041 --> 00:16:04,000
Maybe...

324
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:05,916
I should go.

325
00:16:06,375 --> 00:16:07,750
I'm applying medicine.

326
00:16:10,958 --> 00:16:11,833
Xintian, what is it?

327
00:16:12,791 --> 00:16:14,083
Hua is back.

328
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:19,430
(Yin Manor)

329
00:16:20,083 --> 00:16:21,750
Officer, you...

330
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:23,875
(Jinyiwei Squad Leader
of the Left Qianhu Office)

331
00:16:23,875 --> 00:16:26,208
I'm Shen Bingfan, a Squad Leader
from Jinyiwei Northern Bureau.

332
00:16:26,375 --> 00:16:28,708
I am under orders to arrest Diaotu,
the Flower-Picking Bee.

333
00:16:29,166 --> 00:16:29,750
I need to search the manor.

334
00:16:31,208 --> 00:16:33,083
A Jinyiwei officer is here!

335
00:16:33,083 --> 00:16:34,166
Officer! Officer!

336
00:16:34,541 --> 00:16:35,916
Hua, bad news.

337
00:16:36,083 --> 00:16:37,458
Fan went to Marquis Taiping's manor
alone.

338
00:16:39,310 --> 00:16:40,041
(Yin Xian, Marquis Taiping)

339
00:16:40,041 --> 00:16:40,583
(Yin Xian, Marquis Taiping)
What?

340
00:16:40,791 --> 00:16:41,833
Did I hear that right?

341
00:16:42,041 --> 00:16:43,416
You want to search my manor?

342
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:44,000
My lord,

343
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,000
I suspect

344
00:16:45,250 --> 00:16:47,708
Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee,
is hiding here.

345
00:16:48,125 --> 00:16:49,083
Please allow me to search.

346
00:16:49,083 --> 00:16:49,833
How dare you!

347
00:16:50,125 --> 00:16:51,875
A low-ranking Squad Leader

348
00:16:52,041 --> 00:16:52,916
wants to search my manor?

349
00:16:53,166 --> 00:16:54,416
Do you have an imperial edict

350
00:16:54,416 --> 00:16:55,333
or the Cabinet's gold token?

351
00:16:55,583 --> 00:16:56,708
I am acting under orders
from the Northern Bureau...

352
00:16:56,708 --> 00:16:58,000
To hell with your Northern Bureau!

353
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,083
To hell with it!

354
00:16:59,083 --> 00:16:59,875
Northern Bureau?

355
00:17:00,125 --> 00:17:01,625
No edict. No gold token.

356
00:17:01,875 --> 00:17:03,041
A Squad Leader

357
00:17:03,083 --> 00:17:05,500
dares barge in
and search a marquis's manor?

358
00:17:05,583 --> 00:17:07,791
This is contempt for the court.

359
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:08,583
Guards!

360
00:17:08,666 --> 00:17:09,208
Get her!

361
00:17:09,458 --> 00:17:09,916
Yes, my lord!

362
00:17:11,458 --> 00:17:12,125
Don't you dare.

363
00:17:12,833 --> 00:17:13,750
In this situation,

364
00:17:14,041 --> 00:17:15,333
we need the Commander to step in.

365
00:17:15,666 --> 00:17:16,750
Only he can stand up to Marquis Taiping.

366
00:17:17,166 --> 00:17:18,208
There's one more person who can help.

367
00:17:18,625 --> 00:17:19,666
The Jinyiwei act first

368
00:17:19,833 --> 00:17:20,750
and report later.

369
00:17:21,041 --> 00:17:21,833
It's by imperial authority.

370
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,833
Let me tell you.

371
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:25,083
I'm a first-rank marquis
from a house of merit.

372
00:17:25,125 --> 00:17:27,208
My father won glory
for the empire in battles.

373
00:17:27,333 --> 00:17:28,791
Drawing your blade in my manor

374
00:17:29,458 --> 00:17:30,833
is as good as treason.

375
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:33,041
Lock her up.

376
00:17:33,416 --> 00:17:35,375
Who dares touch
my Northern Bureau officer?

377
00:17:47,458 --> 00:17:48,583
Well, well.

378
00:17:48,875 --> 00:17:50,666
If it isn't the Commander.

379
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:51,541
My lord.

380
00:17:52,416 --> 00:17:54,041
A man of your status

381
00:17:55,291 --> 00:17:57,791
needn't lower himself
to quarrel with a young woman.

382
00:17:58,291 --> 00:17:59,083
You don't understand.

383
00:17:59,416 --> 00:18:00,791
This young woman

384
00:18:01,041 --> 00:18:02,000
came here in broad daylight

385
00:18:02,791 --> 00:18:04,000
to search my manor.

386
00:18:04,583 --> 00:18:06,416
She even used the Northern Bureau
to threaten me.

387
00:18:06,791 --> 00:18:07,875
She accused me

388
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,666
of harboring a wanted outlaw.

389
00:18:11,666 --> 00:18:12,583
This young woman

390
00:18:12,916 --> 00:18:13,916
is no simple girl.

391
00:18:14,791 --> 00:18:15,875
She is new here

392
00:18:16,250 --> 00:18:16,958
and doesn't know the rules.

393
00:18:18,333 --> 00:18:19,083
When we return,

394
00:18:19,708 --> 00:18:21,583
I will punish her severely.

395
00:18:22,333 --> 00:18:22,875
My lord,

396
00:18:23,791 --> 00:18:24,583
would you

397
00:18:25,166 --> 00:18:26,458
do me this favor?

398
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:45,810
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

399
00:18:46,180 --> 00:18:49,560
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

400
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:52,810
♪My heart drifted lost♪

401
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:56,220
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

402
00:18:57,310 --> 00:19:00,520
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

403
00:19:00,930 --> 00:19:04,270
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

404
00:19:04,850 --> 00:19:07,060
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

405
00:19:07,060 --> 00:19:11,100
♪I've softly let it go♪

406
00:19:11,100 --> 00:19:14,970
♪The vow you made was true♪

407
00:19:14,970 --> 00:19:18,720
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

408
00:19:19,020 --> 00:19:20,930
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

409
00:19:20,930 --> 00:19:25,470
♪And forget at world's end♪

410
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:27,270
♪Embracing memory♪

411
00:19:27,270 --> 00:19:29,640
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

412
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:33,520
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

413
00:19:33,520 --> 00:19:35,850
♪I wish to let it pass♪

414
00:19:35,850 --> 00:19:40,850
♪And run toward this vast life♪

